      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum elastic model with nonlinear contact at screw-rod interface accepted as appropriate for static quasi-static loading regime; model form uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "Elastic-plastic titanium alloy constitutive model with penalty-based frictional contact (mu=0.3) at screw-rod interface. Model form validated against prior literature and confirmed appropriate for quasi-static F1717 loading. Sensitivity analysis shows model form contributes <5% to total prediction uncertainty."
