      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and UTS (950 MPa) measured from Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupons from same production lot as test constructs. Screw and rod geometry from CMM measurements (±0.01 mm). Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000)."
